Revision history for Sekhmet

0.01    2026-03-26
        - Initial release
        - ULID generation: ulid(), ulid_binary()
        - Monotonic ULIDs: ulid_monotonic(), ulid_monotonic_binary()
        - Utilities: ulid_time(), ulid_time_ms(), ulid_validate()
        - Conversion: ulid_to_uuid(), uuid_to_ulid()
        - Comparison: ulid_compare()
        - Custom ops on Perl 5.14+, XSUB fallback on 5.8+
        - Built on Horus C primitives (Crockford base32, CSPRNG, timestamps)

